#: /409952fb95fbb825992593fca10961ea_1/index.qmd:21
#, markdown-text
msgid "I am happy to announce that [`canaper`](https://github.com/ropensci/canaper) v1.0.0 is now available on [CRAN](https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/canaper/index.html)! Although I have authored [several R packages](https://www.joelnitta.com/software.html) and made them available via [GitHub](https://github.com/joelnitta/#r-packages-), this is my first original package to be on CRAN."
msgstr "[`canaper`](https://github.com/ropensci/canaper) v1.0.0が[CRAN](https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/canaper/index.html)に登録されました！今までいくつかのRパッケージを書いてGitHubで公開したことがありますが、自分のパッケージがCRANに登録されるのが初めてです。"

#. type: Plain text
